                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>How do you handle seasonal businesses or project-based income?</h3>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>We understand seasonal and project-based business models:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Seasonal Payment Plans:</strong> Repayment schedules aligned with income cycles</li>
                            <li><strong>Line of Credit:</strong> Flexible access during lean periods</li>
                            <li><strong>Project Finance:</strong> Funding tied to specific contracts or projects</li>
                            <li><strong>Annual Assessment:</strong> Evaluate performance over full business cycles</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>We structure finance solutions to match your business patterns rather than forcing standard monthly payments.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3>What compliance and regulatory considerations apply?</h3>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>We ensure full compliance with Australian finance regulations:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>NCCP Compliance:</strong> Full National Consumer Credit Protection compliance</li>
                            <li><strong>ASIC Licensed:</strong> Australian Credit Licence (ACL) authorisation</li>
